<h2>Relevant websites</h2>
<ul>
<li>Beamformit can be obtained from <a href="https://github.com/xanguera/BeamformIt">github</a></li>
<li><a href="http://reverb2014.dereverberation.com">REVERB </a> challenge</li>
<li>A multi-microphone signal processing for speech enhancement completed at
UC Berkeley (ICSI). Has
<a href="http://www1.icsi.berkeley.edu/Speech/papers/multimic/">information</a> on meetings
recorder digits (MRD)
<a href="http://www1.icsi.berkeley.edu/Speech/mr/mrdigits.html">data</a>. Also relates to
the Beamformit tool.</li>
<li>RT 09 challenge <a href="http://www.itl.nist.gov/iad/mig//tests/rt/2009/index.html">NIST evaluation</a></li>
<li><a href="https://sisec.inria.fr">SiSEC </a> challenge</li>
</ul></p>
