<li>C. Knapp and G. Carter, “The generalized correlation method for estimation of
time delay,” <i>IEEE Transactions on Acoustics, Speech, and Signal Processing</i>, vol. 24,
no. 4, pp. 320–327, 1976.<a href="finalpaper2.pdf">[download]</a></li>
<li>Xavier Anguera, Chuck Wooters and Javier Hernando, <i>Acoustic beamforming
for speaker diarization of meetings</i>, IEEE Trans. Audio, Speech, and Lang.
    Proc., Sep. 2007, vol. 15, no. 7, pp.
    2011-2023.<a href="acoustic_beamforming_for_speaker_diarization_of_meetings_TASLP_2007.pdf">[download]</a> </li>
